## 4. SRE Metrics Specification

### 4.1 Service Level Objectives (SLOs)

| Metric | Target | Measurement Window | Burn Rate Alert |
|--------|--------|-------------------|-----------------|
| Availability | 99.95% | 30-day rolling | 14.4x (1h), 6x (6h) |
| Latency p50 | ≤ 85ms | 5-minute rolling | N/A |
| Latency p95 | ≤ 250ms | 5-minute rolling | 3x threshold |
| Latency p99 | ≤ 500ms | 5-minute rolling | 2x threshold |
| Error Rate | ≤ 0.1% | 15-minute rolling | 10x baseline |
| Precedent Match Accuracy | ≥ 94% | 24-hour rolling | 5% degradation |

### 4.2 Service Level Indicators (SLIs)

```yaml
slis:
  availability:
    formula: "(successful_requests / total_requests) × 100"
