## 2. Breakdown Point Score (BPS) Matrix

### 2.1 Risk Classification Schema

```
BPS = (P_failure × I_severity × D_detection⁻¹) / M_mitigation

Where:
- P_failure = Probability of failure (0.0 - 1.0)
- I_severity = Impact severity coefficient (1 - 10)
- D_detection = Detection capability score (1 - 10)
- M_mitigation = Mitigation effectiveness (0.1 - 1.0)
```

### 2.2 Operational Failure Risk Matrix

| Risk ID | Failure Mode | P_failure | I_severity | D_detection | M_mitigation | BPS | Priority |
|---------|--------------|-----------|------------|-------------|--------------|-----|----------|
| BPS-001 | Data Pipeline Corruption | 0.08 | 9 | 7 | 0.85 | 0.121 | P1 |
| BPS-002 | Model Drift Degradation | 0.22 | 7 | 4 | 0.70 | 0.550 | P0 |
| BPS-003 | Input Validation Bypass | 0.05 | 10 | 8 | 0.90 | 0.069 | P2 |
| BPS-004 | Scoring Engine Timeout | 0.15 | 6 | 9 | 0.80 | 0.125 | P1 |
| BPS-005 | Weight Calibration Failure | 0.12 | 8 | 5 | 0.75 | 0.256 | P1 |
| BPS-006 | Bias Amplification Event | 0.18 | 10 | 3 | 0.60 | 1.000 | P0 |
| BPS-007 | Cache Invalidation Race | 0.10 | 4 | 6 | 0.85 | 0.078 | P2 |
| BPS-008 | Feature Store Desync | 0.14 | 7 | 5 | 0.72 | 0.272 | P1 |
| BPS-009 | Inference Latency Spike | 0.25 | 5 | 8 | 0.88 | 0.178 | P1 |
| BPS-010 | Compliance Audit Failure | 0.06 | 10 | 2 | 0.50 | 0.600 | P0 |

### 2.3 BPS Threshold Classifications

```
BPS ∈ [0.000, 0.100) → NOMINAL      → Standard monitoring
BPS ∈ [0.100, 0.300) → ELEVATED     → Enhanced alerting + weekly review
BPS ∈ [0.300, 0.600) → CRITICAL     → Immediate escalation + daily review
BPS ∈ [0.600, 1.000] → CATASTROPHIC → Incident declaration + remediation sprint
```

### 2.4 Cascading Failure Probability Model

```
P_cascade(n) = 1 - ∏(1 - BPSᵢ × Cᵢⱼ) for all connected nodes j

Correlation Matrix Cᵢⱼ:
        BPS-001  BPS-002  BPS-003  BPS-004  BPS-005  BPS-006
BPS-001   1.00     0.35     0.20     0.15     0.40     0.25
BPS-002   0.35     1.00     0.10     0.05     0.65     0.70
BPS-003   0.20     0.10     1.00     0.08     0.15     0.30
BPS-004   0.15     0.05     0.08     1.00     0.12     0.05
BPS-005   0.40     0.65     0.15     0.12     1.00     0.55
BPS-006   0.25     0.70     0.30     0.05     0.55     1.00
```

