# A-CFO-LedgerParser Technical Specification

## System Overview

```
Component ID: A-CFO-LedgerParser
Classification: Financial Data Ingestion Pipeline
Criticality Tier: P0 (Business Critical)
```

---

## 1. Core Logic Architecture

### 1.1 Parser State Machine

```
┌─────────────┐    ┌─────────────┐    ┌─────────────┐    ┌─────────────┐
│   INIT      │───▶│   VALIDATE  │───▶│   PARSE     │───▶│   TRANSFORM │
│   S0        │    │   S1        │    │   S2        │    │   S3        │
└─────────────┘    └─────────────┘    └─────────────┘    └─────────────┘
      │                  │                  │                  │
      ▼                  ▼                  ▼                  ▼
┌─────────────┐    ┌─────────────┐    ┌─────────────┐    ┌─────────────┐
│  ABORT_E0   │    │  REJECT_E1  │    │  ERROR_E2   │    │  COMMIT_S4  │
└─────────────┘    └─────────────┘    └─────────────┘    └─────────────┘
```

### 1.2 Processing Logic Flow

```python
# Pseudocode Logic Block
def process_ledger(input_stream):
    state = S0_INIT

    # Phase 1: Schema Validation
    if not validate_schema(input_stream):
        return (E1_REJECT, null, error_manifest)

    state = S1_VALIDATE

    # Phase 2: Structural Integrity Check
    checksum = compute_sha256(input_stream.payload)
    if checksum != input_stream.metadata.checksum:
        return (E1_REJECT, null, INTEGRITY_FAILURE)

    # Phase 3: Lexical Analysis
    tokens = tokenize(input_stream.payload)
    if token_error_rate(tokens) > 0.001:
        return (E2_ERROR, partial_result, token_errors)

    state = S2_PARSE

    # Phase 4: Semantic Parsing
    ast = build_ledger_ast(tokens)
    entries = extract_journal_entries(ast)

    # Phase 5: Balance Verification
    for entry in entries:
        if abs(sum(entry.debits) - sum(entry.credits)) > EPSILON:
            flag_imbalance(entry)

    state = S3_TRANSFORM

    # Phase 6: Normalization
    normalized = normalize_to_canonical(entries)

    state = S4_COMMIT
    return (S4_COMMIT, normalized, null)
```

