## 3. Breakdown Point Score (BPS) Matrix

### 3.1 BPS Calculation Formula

```
BPS(component) = Σ(Pᵢ × Iᵢ × Dᵢ) / 100

Where:
  Pᵢ = Probability of failure (0-100)
  Iᵢ = Impact severity (1-10)
  Dᵢ = Detection difficulty (1-10)

Risk Classification:
  BPS ∈ [0, 50)    → LOW
  BPS ∈ [50, 150)  → MEDIUM
  BPS ∈ [150, 300) → HIGH
  BPS ≥ 300        → CRITICAL
```

